      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNOOZY DONUT (3) flew the lids off the inside draw with a sensational early split last time and gave a sight, finishing a 2.5 lengths second (25.36) over 450m at this track. Top chance in this line up. KIWI EDDIE (5) made light work of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (28.34) at Bendigo over 500m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can measure up. TWO TRUTHS (1) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Rank Limit - Maiden win two back (23.98) at Bendigo. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. SHAGGY BEAR (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around.",
